# FvwmButtons - LeftPanel
#
# FvwmButtons is a powerful module that can be used to build custom
# panels and docks. This config uses FvwmButtons to build the LeftPanel.
# The panel contains buttons to switch desks, FvwmPager, a system tray,
# FvwmIconMan (list of running windows), and a clock.
#
# Note - To use the system tray you must have "stalonetray" installed.

Style LeftPanel !Title, BorderWidth 2, HandleWidth 2, Sticky, WindowListSkip, CirculateSkip, NeverFocus, StaysOnBottom, Sticky

DestroyModuleConfig LeftPanel:*
# *LeftPanel: Geometry 120x$[vp.height]+2+2
*LeftPanel: Geometry 156x144-4+4
*LeftPanel: Colorset 10
*LeftPanel: Rows $[vp.height]
*LeftPanel: Columns 120
*LeftPanel: Frame 0
*LeftPanel: Font "xft:Roboto Mono:style=Regular:size=11:antialias=true"
#*LeftPanel: (120x45, Icon "fvwm-logo-small.png", Frame 0)
#*LeftPanel: (120x5, Frame 0)
#*LeftPanel: (10x20, Frame 0)
*LeftPanel: (30x20, Id desk0, Title "1", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 0, Colorset 11, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 0)
*LeftPanel: (30x20, Id desk1, Title "2", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 1, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 0)
*LeftPanel: (30x20, Id desk2, Title "3", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 2, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 0)
*LeftPanel: (30x20, Id desk3, Title "4", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 3, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 0)
#*LeftPanel: (10x20, Frame 0)
#*LeftPanel: (5x60, Frame 0)
#*LeftPanel: (120x5, Frame 0)
*LeftPanel: (120x60, Swallow FvwmPager 'Module FvwmPager *', Frame 1)
#*LeftPanel: (5x80, Frame 0)
#*LeftPanel: (120x5, Frame 0)
#Test (x stalonetray) *LeftPanel: (120x20, Swallow(NoClose,UseOld) stalonetray \
#'Exec exec stalonetray --config "$[FVWM_DATADIR]/default-config/.stalonetrayrc"', Frame 0)
#Test (x stalonetray) PipeRead 'echo "*LeftPanel: (120x$(($[vp.height]-225)), 
#Top, Swallow FvwmIconMan \'Module FvwmIconMan\', Frame 0)"'
#Test (!x stalonetray) PipeRead 'echo "*LeftPanel: (120x$(($[vp.height]-205)),\
#    Top, Swallow FvwmIconMan \'Module FvwmIconMan\', Frame 0)"'
*LeftPanel: (120x30, Swallow DateTime 'Module FvwmScript FvwmScript-DateTime', Frame 0)
# *LeftPanel: (120x5, Frame 0)


Style ButtonLaunchers !Title, HandleWidth 3, BorderWidth 3, WindowListSkip, CirculateSkip, StaysOnBottom, NeverFocus, Sticky

DestroyModuleConfig ButtonLaunchers
*ButtonLaunchers: Geometry 300x48+2-2
*ButtonLaunchers: Colorset 14
*ButtonLaunchers: Columns 6
*ButtonLaunchers: Rows 1
*ButtonLaunchers: Frame 1
*ButtonLaunchers: Font "xft:Sans:Regular:size=9:antialias=True"
*ButtonLaunchers: (1x1, Title "", Icon "icons/apps/cats_tr.png", Action `Exec jgmenu --config-file=/home/doug/.config/jgmenu/jgfvwmrc`)
*ButtonLaunchers: (1x1, Title "", Icon "icons/apps/network-server.png", Action `Exec thunar`)
*ButtonLaunchers: (1x1, Title "", Icon "icons/apps/terminix.png", Action `Exec urxvt`)
*ButtonLaunchers: (1x1, Title "", Icon "icons/apps/sublime-text.png" Action `Exec subl3`)
*ButtonLaunchers: (1x1, Title "", Icon "icons/apps/firefox32.png" Action `Exec firefox`)
*ButtonLaunchers: (1x1, Title "", Icon "icons/apps/mail.png" Action `Exec thunderbird`)

Style DeskTopId !Title, BorderWidth 3, HandleWidth 3, Sticky, CirculateSkip, WindowListSkip, NeverFocus, StaysOnBottom, Sticky

DestroyModuleConfig DeskTopId:*
*DeskTopId: Geometry 192x48-2+2
*DeskTopId: Colorset 14
*DeskTopId: Rows 1
*DeskTopId: Columns 4
*DeskTopId: Frame 0
*DeskTopId: Font "xft:Roboto Mono:style=Regular:size=11:antialias=true"
#*DeskTopId: (10x20, Frame 0)
*DeskTopId: (1x1, Id desk0, Title "1", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 0, Colorset 11, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 0)
*DeskTopId: (1x1, Id desk1, Title "2", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 1, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 0)
*DeskTopId: (1x1, Id desk2, Title "3", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 2, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 0)
*DeskTopId: (1x1, Id desk3, Title "4", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 3, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 0)
#*DeskTopId: (10x20, Frame 0)

